name: Basil Korea 2DFilter
description:
It's a merge of some popular checkpoint based on Basil Korea to create 2D aesthetic

  • Use hires fix

  • Use DPM ++ SDE Karras

  • Use ERSGAN 4X+Anime 6B

  • Use 4 CFG

  • Use Use 0.4 denoise

  • Use 10 hires steps

  • Clip Skip:2

  • Use VAE

You can experiment it all you want, the guide above is basically my template to use the checkpoint
